    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just being tired though. it's the feeling that the cycle is inevitable. no matter how much I \"rest\" or \"gather strength,\" the loop just starts over. it feels like a glitch in my life. like the more I struggle, the more it just proves that nothing is ever going to change. everything i do leads back to the same zero.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
